data.description: Beautiful corner lot home located in Silver Lake.  Fully fenced yard, mature landscape, low maintenance. New LVP floors on main level, office space, living room, dining room, spacious kitchen, mud room and guest bath.  Upstairs there is a generous loft, large master with spa like master bath, two additional bedrooms, another full bath and laundry. All bedrooms have large walk-in closets. The basement is large and ready for someone to put their personal touches on. Home has a new hot water heater, a water softener and all windows wells have coverings. Home is now and has been covered under a home warranty since 2019.
